OL,5, Four presenters have begun legal action
OL,6, against the BBC on grounds of sex and  
OL,7, age discrimination and equal pay.      
OL,9,FMartine Croxall, Annita McVeigh, Karin 
OL,10,FGiannone and Kasia Madera are attending
OL,11,Fa two-day hearing for an employment    
OL,12,Ftribunal against the corporation in    
OL,13,Fcentral London.                        
OL,15,FThey claim they lost their roles on the
OL,16,FBBC News Channel following a "rigged"  
OL,17,Frecruitment exercise.                  
OL,19,FThe BBC insists its application process
OL,20,Fwas "rigorous and fair".               
